<LP>
   AUSTIN, Texas -- Southern Union Co. said it hired
Donaldson, Lufkin &amp; Jenrette Securities Corp. to advise it on
the possible sale of its Southern Union Exploration Co. unit
as a means of enhancing shareholder value.
   The natural gas concern said the advisers will consider
various alternatives for the unit, including a sale of
existing production and reserves.
